Runway incursion events are reported by the respective air traffic control tower. The data reflect the ICAO definition of a runway incursion as well as the related severity categories. The runway incursion database is maintained by the FAA Office of Runway Safety.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>airports</dcat:keyword>         <dcat:keyword>faa</dcat:keyword>
